Simple Bean implementations of Payu Config Every payu Async tasks require Config object data Should be the final data, which will be posted on payu server environment Should be the environment. PayuConstants.MOBILE_STAGING_ENV PayuConstants.PRODUCTION_ENV PayuConstants.STAGING_ENV if none of the evn specified sdk will point to PayuConstants.PRODUCTION_ENV
